<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_418_r1l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>Fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> habt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> von 
<del rend="strikethrough"> dem<expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l21">
<del rend="strikethrough">durchleẅchtıgı </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc künıgs <expan>Reͣte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l22"><expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu Colldıcʒ / vnd <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hartung Clux / <expan>ʒuuerſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l23">Das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l24">vns <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> von Colldıcʒ wırte bey vns geſagt hat / daʒ dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l25">Reͣte . noch nıht bey vns <expan>fürgerıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn / doch ſo ſey Jm von </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_419" id="208v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l1">des von Colldıcʒ <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etlıch ſache <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> . dabey er ſıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehe</expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l2">der von Colldıcʒ bey vns fürreıten <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . / Ob <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> das alſo beſchehe oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l3">wenn oder auf welch ʒeıt . Des wıſſen wır noch der <expan>eg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> wırt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_r1l4">kein eygenſchaft auf dıſʒ ʒeıt . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_419_line_1577282814734_6624"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_418" id="208r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
